", "newText": "            System.setProperty(propertyName, ContentTypeHandler.class.getName());\n            currentThread.setContextClassLoader(MimeUtilTest.class.getClassLoader());\n            String contentType = part.getContentType();\n\n            assertThat(contentType).isEqualTo(\"text/plain; charset=utf-8\");\n"}, {"oldText": "\n    private static final class RejectingClassLoader extends ClassLoader {\n        private final Set<String> rejectedNames;\n        private final List<String> rejectedLoads;\n\n        private RejectingClassLoader(ClassLoader parent, Set<String> rejectedNames) {\n            super(parent);\n            this.rejectedNames = rejectedNames;\n            this.rejectedLoads = new ArrayList<>();\n        }\n\n        @Override\n        public Class<?> loadClass(String name) throws ClassNotFoundException {\n            if (rejectedNames.contains(name)) {\n                rejectedLoads.add(name);\n                throw new ClassNotFoundException(name);\n            }\n            return super.loadClass(name);\n        }\n\n        private List<String> getRejectedLoads() {\n            return rejectedLoads;\n        }\n    }\n", "newText": ""}]}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 903, "output": 1597, "cacheRead": 35840, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 38340, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1778511515481, "responseId": "resp_02d20df727719d4e016a01ee9c9700819cb066b6b98bda5311"}, "toolResults": [{"role": "toolResult", "toolCallId": "call_UTB7SOz7w77N10Lj7qhZQPhU|fc_02d20df727719d4e016a01eead0d88819c98075db0ef139a99", "toolName": "edit", "content": [{"type": "text", "text": "Could not find edits[0] in tests/src/jakarta.platform/jakarta.jakartaee-api/10.0.0/src/test/java/jakarta_platform/jakarta_jakartaee_api/MimeUtilTest.java. The oldText must match exactly including all whitespace and newlines."}], "deta